## ğŸ“Š Observability & Monitoring
- Correlation IDs for tracing requests end-to-end.  
- Redaction of tokens and sensitive data in logs.  
- Crash reporting (Sentry/Expo) optional, anonymized.  
- Lighthouse + Playwright security checks automated in CI/CD.  

