## ğŸ“‹ Compliance
- GDPR & CCPA transparency: Privacy Policy accessible in-app and on website.  
- Google Play Data Safety: microphone optional, no unnecessary permissions.  
- Apple App Store Privacy Nutrition Labels: accurate, no hidden data use.  
- Cookie consent banner (for Web, if analytics enabled).  
- Regular penetration testing and dependency scanning (npm audit, Semgrep, Gitleaks).  

